  "title": "Warehouse Assistant [Woodlands | 5 days | shift work | up to $3000] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Warehouse Assistant</strong></h3><p><strong>5 days, 9am-6pm (in swing shift off, eg: Friday & Sat/ Sun & Mon), need to standby at night (call standby only, will have standby allowance)</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2400- $3000</strong></p><p><strong>Location:  Woodlands, N Coast Dr, Singapore 757432 (Station in Micron)</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Preparing parts that customer send out everyday</li><li>Receive part and update into inventory </li><li>Daily part move in/out update</li><li>Order part follow forecast </li><li>Inspect the used parts and send the reuse parts for cleaning</li><li>Use of pallet jet and trolley</li><li>Replying emails</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Good in Ms Word and Excel for data record, and able to reply simple email</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
